## 
## @tutorial(Authenticating Users): https://github.com/IronBrandon/Godot-GameJolt-API#authenticating-users
## @tutorial(Unlocking Trophies): https://github.com/IronBrandon/Godot-GameJolt-API#unlocking-trophies
